<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Hackathon Results Published</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f4f7f6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #eee;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .result-card {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            border-left: 4px solid #3498db;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .result-item {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .result-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #7f8c8d;
            width: 120px;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        .result-value {
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #bdc3c7;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            padding-top: 20px;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #2980b9;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Congratulations!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <%= userName %>,</p>
            <p>The results for <strong><%= hackathonTitle %></strong> have been published. We are excited to share your performance with you!</p>
            
            <div class="result-card">
                <div class="result-item">
                    <span class="result-label">Submission:</span>
                    <span class="result-value"><%= submissionTitle %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="result-item">
                    <span class="result-label">Rank:</span>
                    <span class="result-value">#<%= rank %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="result-item">
                    <span class="result-label">Award:</span>
                    <span class="result-value"><%= awardCategory %></span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <p>We want to thank you for your incredible effort and participation. Every line of code contributes to the innovation of our community.</p>
            
            <% if (certificateUrl) { %>
            <p>You can download your certificate of achievement below:</p>
            <a href="<%= certificateUrl %>" class="btn">Download Certificate</a>
            <% } %>

            <p>Or visit the hackathon page to see the full leaderboard:</p>
            <a href="<%= resultsLink %>" style="color: #3498db; text-decoration: underline;">View Full Results</a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Athenura Hackathon Platform. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
